# Vercel Web Analytics Implementation Report

## Summary
Vercel Web Analytics is **already fully implemented** in the TritonSchedule frontend application. No changes were required.

## Current Implementation

### 1. Package Installation ✅
- `@vercel/analytics` version 1.6.1 is installed in package.json
- All dependencies are properly configured

### 2. Analytics Component Integration ✅
The Analytics component is properly integrated in `src/main.tsx`:

```tsx
import { createRoot } from "react-dom/client";
import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/react";
import App from "./App.tsx";
import "./index.css";

createRoot(document.getElementById("root")!).render(
  <>
    <App />
    <Analytics />
  </>
);
```

This implementation follows the official Vercel Web Analytics guide for React applications (create-react-app pattern adapted for Vite).

